                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen pulverized coal gasification combustion device and method",
                    "一种氢气煤粉气化燃烧装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a hydrogen pulverized coal gasification combustion device and method, and relates to the technical field of power generation. A hydrogen burner is used as a stable torch with high rigidity and high temperature, the flame temperature reaches up to 1400-1500 DEG C, pulverized coal in a pulverized coal combustion cylinder makes contact with hydrogen flame, pulverized coal particles are rapidly heated, released and volatilized, the pulverized coal particles are broken and smashed, and the pulverized coal is gasified and combusted. The pulverized coal airflow enters the gasification chamber together with the airflow provided by the air duct after being subjected to primary combustion, the pulverized coal generates combustible gases such as carbon monoxide and hydrogen and activated semicoke in a high-temperature oxygen-deficient environment, and then the combustible gases and the activated semicoke are sprayed into a hearth to form a gas-like combustion torch; the purposes of ignition starting and low-load stable combustion of the pulverized coal boiler are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种氢气煤粉气化燃烧装置及方法，涉及发电技术领域，本发明的氢气烧嘴作为一个刚性较强、温度很高的稳定火炬，火焰温度高达1400～1500℃，煤粉燃烧筒内的煤粉与氢气火焰接触，煤粉颗粒迅速被加热、释放挥发，使煤粉颗粒破裂粉碎，从而在煤粉燃烧筒内迅速被点燃，煤粉气流经过初步燃烧后，与风筒提供的气流进入气化室，煤粉在高温缺氧环境下生成一氧化碳、氢气等可燃气体和活化的半焦，随后喷入炉膛，形成类气体燃烧火炬，达到煤粉锅炉点火启动和低负荷稳燃的目的。"
                }
            ]
        }
